Package smarthome.domain.room

Class Room

java.lang.Object
smarthome.domain.room.Room
All Implemented Interfaces:
AggregateRoot<RoomId>, DomainEntity<RoomId>
public class Room extends Object implements AggregateRoot<RoomId>
Represents a room within a smart home environment. A room is considered an aggregate root in the domain-driven design context, uniquely identified by a RoomId. It also includes additional attributes such as RoomName its designation, the HouseName it belongs to, its location within the house as indicated by Floor, and its physical Dimensions.
